            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "In Agriculture Department, Rajasthan Government has started the Diggy Scheme to provide subsidies to the farmers of Rajasthan for making dig for irrigation. Under the scheme, farmers can prepare ways in their fields collect water in one place, and do more irrigation with the help of sprinklers. By providing this grant amount to the farmers, the government will encourage the farmers to grow good crops by building dig and irrigating the crops without any financial pressure. This scheme is to help farmers improve their farming by using more water resources and encourage them to grow good crops."
